{"article_id":"8nOnzrOtNRG6O6Ki","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"An elite crew of firefighters","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"trained","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to battle the nation 's fiercest wildfires","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"was overtaken by an out-of-control blaze in Arizona ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"killing 19 members","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"as they tried to protect themselves from the flames under fire-resistant shields .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"It was the most firefighters","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"killed","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"battling a wildfire in the U.S. in decades .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"The lightning-sparked fire ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"which spread to at least 2,000 acres amid triple-digit temperatures ,","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"also destroyed 200 homes","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"and sent hundreds fleeing from Yarnell , a town of about 700 residents about 85 miles northwest of Phoenix .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Residents huddled in shelters and bars ,","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"watching their homes burn on TV","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"as flames lit up the night sky in the forest above the town .","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"\" My heart weeps for those","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"who lost their lives","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"and were affected by today ' s Yarnell Hill Fire .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"My thoughts and prayers go out to the families","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"who have lost so much","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"and the first responders","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"battling this difficult situation .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"I urge others to join me","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"in keeping those affected by this tragic fire in our thoughts and prayers .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"My office and I will continue to closely monitor the situation","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"and remain in communication with emergency responders .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Please do not hesitate to contact my office","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"if we can be of assistance . \"","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"May the Members of Granite Mountain Hotshots rest in peace .","depth":3},{"id":30,"text":"RT @ JordanGhawi :","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"19 brothers .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Gone .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"pic.twitter.com/yogoj1D0d8 # Yarnell","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"- Cathy O'Neill","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"( @ CAO916 )","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"July 1 , 2013","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"`` They died heroes","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"and we 'll miss them .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"We love them . ''","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Wife of fallen firefighter , Juliann Ashcraft , mother of 4","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"- Rebekah L. Sanders","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"( @ RebekahLSanders )","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"July 1 , 2013","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"A hat hanging on the fence at Prescott Fire Station 7 above a bouquet of flowers ...","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"pic.twitter.com/QmByZuuYG6","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"- Emma Jade","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"( @ emmajade12news )","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"July 1 , 2013","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Late Sunday evening , 19 Granite Mountain Hot Shot Crew members were killed","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"as they attempted to control a wildfire","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that burned down half of Yarnell , Arizona .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"This is the largest loss of firefighters since 9/11/2001.","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Arizona Congressman Paul Gosar ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"whose district covers Yarnell ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"issued the following statement late last night in response to the horrific news.","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Many on Twitter gave their condolences and prayers.","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Hot shot crews are highly trained","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"and used all over the West","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"to combat wildfires every year .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Just last week , the training and preparedness of the Granite Mountain Hot Shot Crew was profiled by The Daily Courier .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"May they rest in peace .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":123,"left":77,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":70,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":67,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":65,"right":66,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":64,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":0,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":6,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":73,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":15,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":89,"right":121,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":89,"left":83,"right":88,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":83,"left":79,"right":82,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":79,"left":16,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":82,"left":80,"right":81,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":80,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left